CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 25, 1963, pg. 6, reads: "Gala Occasion - The home of Mrs. W.W. Gittens was the scene of festivity last Saturday when several members of the Semper Fidelis Club and Pi Chapter of Iota Phi Lambda Sorority gave a party for Mmes. Helane Wilson, Iva Johnson and Catherine Dix. Left to right, first row: Mrs. W.W.Gittens, Hazel Garland, Dolores Epps, Phyllis Kelley (oldest member of Semper Fidelis Club), Jean Dix, president of Semper Fidelis; Katie Johnson, Adell Long, Marilyn Baldwin, Mildred Peyton and Florence Ball Jones, president of the Iotas.  Back row: Mmes. Charlotte Pangburn, Delgratia Allen, Jeanne Farrish, Anne Penn, Grace Johnson, Mary Johnson, Myrtle Still, Frances Keith Newman, Helena Wilson, Ethel Christian, Iva Johnson, Pauline Coles, and Catherine Dix. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Semper Fidelis Club and Pi Chapter of Iota Phi Lambda sorority members, first row from left: Mrs. W. W. Gittens, Hazel Garland, Dolores Epps, Phyllis Kelley, Jean Dix, Katie Johnson, Adell Long, Marilyn Baldwin, Mildred Peyton, Florence Ball Jones; back row: Charlotte Pangburn, Delgratia Allen, Jeanne Farrish, Anne Penn, Grace Johnson, Mary Johnson, Myrtle Still, Frances Keith Newman, Helane Wilson, Ethel Christian, Iva Johnson, Pauline Coles, and Catherine Dix, gathered for party in Gittens home
